HEADWORD: Piscina
<hw>Pis*ci"na</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a certain,
fishpond, fr. <ets>piscis</ets> a fish.]</ety> <fld>(Arch.)</fld> <def>A
